2021-10-09T22:13:25Z	(#u4bhkvq) My template ([most recent copy](https://clbin.com/5g9kS)) attempts to solve the latter two problems, but I think it's another job for `awk` to avoid the dumpster fire below.  ``` timestamp=$(echo "$line" | grep -Eo '^[0-9]{4}-[01][0-9]-[0-3][0-9][Tt][0-2][0-9]:[0-5][0-9]:[0-5][0-9](\.[0-9]+)?([+-][0-2][0-9]:[0-5][0-9]|Zz)') twt=$(echo "$line" | sed -e 's/"/\"/g; s/```/\`/g' | cut -f 2- -) hyperlinked=$(echo "$twt" | sed 's|http://[^ ]*[^ ,.;:)>}!]|<a href="&">&</a>|g; s|https://[^ ]*[^ ,.;:)>}!]|<a href="&">&</a>|g') ```
